(1592, 401, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"d8a0981\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"43da2ab\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress-june\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/biographie-june-peduzzi-5-scaled.jpg\",\"id\":520},\"image_size\":\"1536x1536\",\"caption_source\":\"attachment\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\",\"opacity\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.8,\"sizes\":[]},\"opacity_hover\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"79d0bfc\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress-june\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/cv-june-peduzzi-scaled.jpg\",\"id\":530},\"image_size\":\"1536x1536\",\"opacity\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.9,\"sizes\":[]},\"opacity_hover\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"b83bc6f\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8ef2f1e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress-june\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/City-Sonic-logo.png\",\"id\":549},\"image_size\":\"medium\",\"caption_source\":\"attachment\",\"link_to\":\"custom\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/citysonic.be\\/festival2019\\/june-peduzzi\\/\",\"is_external\":\"on\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"6720a27\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"T\\u00e9l\\u00e9 Banque Hypnose (vid\\u00e9o)\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/citysonic.be\\/festival2019\\/june-peduzzi\\/\",\"is_external\":\"on\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"},\"_flex_align_self\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"eead0f8\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Sur un texte d\\u2019<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/citysonic.be\\/festival2019\\/antoine-boute\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Antoine Boute<\\/a>, une cr\\u00e9ation sonore de\\u00a0<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/citysonic.be\\/festival2019\\/vincent-matyn\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Vincent Matyn<\\/a>\\u00a0et des images de\\u00a0<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/citysonic.be\\/festival2019\\/june-peduzzi\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">June Peduzzi<\\/a>. Une oeuvre collective qui s\\u2019est constitu\\u00e9e par \\u00e9tape.<\\/p><p>Un texte, \\u2018Op\\u00e9ration Biohardcore\\u2019 aux \\u00e9ditions\\u00a0<em>Les petits matins<\\/em>\\u00a0a inspir\\u00e9 une fiction sonore (produit par Radio Panik).Celle-ci demandait une extension visuelle pour une installation cin\\u00e9ma immersive.<\\/p><p>Un conte, un jeu d\\u2019ombres et de lumi\\u00e8res mettant en sc\\u00e8ne notre rapport aux m\\u00e9dias, \\u00e0 la s\\u00e9duction technologique et implicitement au capitalisme et \\u00e0 la finance. Un conte philosophico-burlesque. Plusieurs formes se croisent ici : la dramatique radio, le conte et la composition \\u00e9lectro-acoustique. Cinq chapitres qui invitent \\u00e0 penser notre relation \\u00e0 l\\u2019argent, \\u00e0 la communication, au pouvoir.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
