(401, 1, '2023-02-03 08:42:10', '2023-02-03 07:42:10', '<style>/*! elementor - v3.10.2 - 29-01-2023 */\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>									<figure>\n										<img width=\"1086\" height=\"1536\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/biographie-june-peduzzi-5-1086x1536.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/biographie-june-peduzzi-5-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/biographie-june-peduzzi-5-212x300.jpg 212w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/biographie-june-peduzzi-5-724x1024.jpg 724w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/biographie-june-peduzzi-5-768x1086.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/biographie-june-peduzzi-5-1448x2048.jpg 1448w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/biographie-june-peduzzi-5-scaled.jpg 1810w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1086px) 100vw, 1086px\" />											<figcaption></figcaption>\n										</figure>\n															<img width=\"1086\" height=\"1536\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cv-june-peduzzi-1086x1536.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cv-june-peduzzi-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cv-june-peduzzi-212x300.jpg 212w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cv-june-peduzzi-724x1024.jpg 724w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cv-june-peduzzi-768x1086.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cv-june-peduzzi-1448x2048.jpg 1448w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cv-june-peduzzi-scaled.jpg 1810w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1086px) 100vw, 1086px\" />															\n												<figure>\n											<a href=\"http://citysonic.be/festival2019/june-peduzzi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n							<img width=\"300\" height=\"143\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/City-Sonic-logo-300x143.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/City-Sonic-logo-300x143.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress-june/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/City-Sonic-logo.png 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />								</a>\n											<figcaption></figcaption>\n										</figure>\n			<style>/*! elementor - v3.10.2 - 29-01-2023 */\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}</style><h2><a href=\"http://citysonic.be/festival2019/june-peduzzi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Télé Banque Hypnose (vidéo)</a></h2>		\n		<p>Sur un texte d’<a href=\"http://citysonic.be/festival2019/antoine-boute/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Antoine Boute</a>, une création sonore de <a href=\"http://citysonic.be/festival2019/vincent-matyn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vincent Matyn</a> et des images de <a href=\"http://citysonic.be/festival2019/june-peduzzi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">June Peduzzi</a>. Une oeuvre collective qui s’est constituée par étape.</p><p>Un texte, ‘Opération Biohardcore’ aux éditions <em>Les petits matins</em> a inspiré une fiction sonore (produit par Radio Panik).Celle-ci demandait une extension visuelle pour une installation cinéma immersive.</p><p>Un conte, un jeu d’ombres et de lumières mettant en scène notre rapport aux médias, à la séduction technologique et implicitement au capitalisme et à la finance. Un conte philosophico-burlesque. Plusieurs formes se croisent ici : la dramatique radio, le conte et la composition électro-acoustique. Cinq chapitres qui invitent à penser notre relation à l’argent, à la communication, au pouvoir.</p>', 'about', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-2', '', '', '2023-02-03 15:31:06', '2023-02-03 14:31:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress-june/?page_id=401', 0, 'page', '', 0),
